    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-03-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-03-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="107" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d107">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Dun</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 109.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the
                                    United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Li Hung Chang’s speedy recovery anticipated. Early resumption of negotiations
                        probable.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
